text: Rudy Rinaldi (born 18 August 1993) is a Monegasque bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Monegasque male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Monaco Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Competitors at the 2012 Winter Youth Olympics
